text: Baba Gurinder Singh (born 1954) is the spiritual head of Radha Soami Satsang Beas. Gurinder Singh may also refer to: * Gurinder Singh (cricketer) (born 1992), Indian cricketer * Gurinder Singh (field hockey) (born 1995), Indian field hockey player * Gurinder Singh (volleyball) (born 1989), Indian volleyball player
title: Gurinder Singh (disambiguation)
